<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
老實說，<delay8 />我仔細考慮過了，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得我想要離開這座島！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" /><delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住起來<delay8 />
的確很舒適，是座很棒的島！<delay40 />但是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想住在其他的島上看看呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你留在這裡啦！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這樣啊……</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />那個啊……<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我打算近期就要<delay8 />
離開這座島了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />待在這裡<delay8 />雖然非常舒服，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我想說<delay8 />我差不多也該出去冒險，<delay20 />
尋求新的邂逅了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不可以走！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要保重喔……</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實說，<delay8 />我有件事<delay20 />
想要特別先跟你說耶。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是……我在這座島上<delay8 />也創造了許多回憶，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我認真在考慮<delay20 />
是不是該搬去新的地方啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不要走！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">原來是這樣</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你希望我留下來啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚嗚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />你都這樣說了，<delay20 />
這樣我實在<delay8 />捨不得走啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然這樣<delay8 />我就別搬家，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />繼續在這島上<delay8 />多待一陣子啦。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後也請你多多關照囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay20 />聽到別人這樣說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在讓人不忍心就這樣離開呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看我還是不要搬家好啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要離開島上，<delay20 />還是等我跟你
再多聊聊各種話題之後再說吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦哦，<delay20 />沒想到你竟然會這樣說，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還真是個重情義的人呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你<delay8 />願意挽留我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你都這樣說了，<delay20 />
我怎麼還捨得<delay8 />離開這裡啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來搬家的事<delay8 />就先暫且擱置吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你一直以來<delay8 />都願意當我的好朋友。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我早就知道，<delay20 />你這麼替人著想，<delay8 />
想必不會硬是挽留我的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管之後我去了哪裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這座島上度過的日子<delay8 />
都永遠會是<delay8 />我珍貴的寶物喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興<delay8 />能跟你當好朋友喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了別讓我<delay8 />捨不得離開這裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啟程的那天，<delay8 />你可要帶著笑容為我送行啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來我還要打包搬家的行李，<delay8 />
總覺得應該會有很多事要忙，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次有空的話，<delay8 />再來找我聊天吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在<tag a="110" b="33" />上的生活<delay8 />
實在是有太多快樂的事了，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很慶幸，當初搬來這裡真是太好了。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的是，<delay20 />我還能遇到你呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很謝謝你<delay8 />願意當我的好朋友哩！<delay20 />
你今後也要和大家好好地生活喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>